{"translation-revision-date":"2025-02-04T15:33:29+00:00","generator":"WP-CLI\/2.12.0","source":"admin-core\/assets\/build\/onboarding-app.js","domain":"messages","locale_data":{"messages":{"":{"domain":"messages","lang":"en","plural-forms":"nplurals=2; plural=(n != 1);"},"Spectra":["Spectra"],"Elementor":["Elementor"],"Bricks":["Bakstenen"],"Other":["Anders"],"Email address":["E-mailadres"],"Reset":["Opnieuw instellen"],"Processing":["Verwerken"],"Access all of our pro templates when you upgrade your plan to CartFlows Pro today.":["Toegang tot al onze pro-sjablonen wanneer je je plan vandaag nog upgrade naar CartFlows Pro."],"Get CartFlows Pro":["Koop CartFlows Pro"],"Back":["Terug"],"Importing..":["Importeren.."],"Active":["Actief"],"Let's Start":["Laten we beginnen"],"Welcome to CartFlows":["Welkom bij CartFlows"],"You're only minutes away from having a more profitable WooCommerce store! This short setup wizard will help you get started with CartFlows.":["Je bent nog maar een paar minuten verwijderd van een winstgevendere WooCommerce-winkel! Deze korte installatiewizard helpt je op weg met CartFlows."],"Save & Continue":["Opslaan & Doorgaan"],"Saving":["Opslaan"],"Hi there! Tell us which page builder you use.":["Hoi daar! Vertel ons welke paginabouwer je gebruikt."],"Install & Activate":["Installeren & Activeren"],"Installing Required Plugins":["Vereiste plug-ins installeren"],"Since CartFlows uses WooCommerce, we'll set it up for you along with Cart Abandonment and Stripe Payments so you can recover abandoned orders and easily accept payments.":["Aangezien CartFlows gebruikmaakt van WooCommerce, zullen we het voor je instellen samen met Cart Abandonment en Stripe Payments, zodat je verlaten bestellingen kunt terughalen en eenvoudig betalingen kunt accepteren."],"Continuing\u2026":["Doorgaan\u2026"],"Continue":["Doorgaan"],"First Name":["Voornaam"],"Please enter your name":["Voer uw naam in"],"Enter Your Email":["Voer uw e-mailadres in"],"Please Enter Name":["Voer