cept payments easily with Stripe integration":[""],"Works seamlessly with your existing page builder":[""],"Boost revenue with upsells, downsells, and order bumps":[""],"CartFlows \u2014 Welcome Walkthrough":[""],"Get Started with Onboarding":[""],"CartFlows works with all page builders, so don't worry if your page builder is not in the list.":[""],"Great job! Now let's install some required plugins.":[""],"Not Installed":[""],"Previous templates":[""],"Next templates":[""],"One last step.":[""],"Let's setup email reports on how your store is doing.":[""],"Let CartFlows take the guesswork out of your checkout results. Each week your store will send you an email report with key metrics and insights. You also will receive emails from us to help your store sell more.":[""],"Help improve CartFlows by sharing non-sensitive usage data.":[""],"We don't collect any personal information\u2014just basic details like your PHP version, admin language, and which features you use.":[""],"Learn more":[""],"about what we collect and why.":[""],"High-converting checkout pages":[""],"Your store now has optimized checkout pages ready to convert visitors into customers.":[""],"Cart abandonment recovery":[""],"Automatically recover lost sales with built-in cart abandonment emails.":[""],"Revenue-boosting funnels":[""],"Upsells, downsells, and order bumps are ready to maximize your average order value.":[""],"Congratulations, You Did it! \ud83c\udf89":[""],"CartFlows is set up on your website! You're now ready to build high-converting sales funnels.":[""],"Here's What You've Unlocked:":[""],"Redirecting\u2026":[""],"Go To Dashboard":[""]}}}